2026-05-15T00:47:38.1940693Z 223        <!--
2026-05-15T00:47:38.1941258Z 224            Override Google Play Billing's ProxyBillingActivity so the system
2026-05-15T00:47:38.1942082Z 225            cannot restore it from Recents or after process death with a
2026-05-15T00:47:38.1943132Z 226            stale Intent. The library's onCreate reads the PendingIntent
2026-05-15T00:47:38.1943920Z 227            extra without null-checking; if Android recreates the activity
2026-05-15T00:47:38.1944828Z 228            and the extra is missing, it NPEs on
2026-05-15T00:47:38.1945543Z 229            PendingIntent.getIntentSender(). noHistory + excludeFromRecents
2026-05-15T00:47:38.1946357Z 230            ensures the activity is finished as soon as it leaves the
2026-05-15T00:47:38.1947126Z 231            foreground and is never re-entered with a missing extra. See
2026-05-15T00:47:38.1947954Z 232            crash report tagged "ProxyBillingActivity NPE" for context.
